name: Hotel Hermitage
descriptionTitle: Alojate en el corazon de Bogotá
description: Hermoso hotel 5 estrellas Caticus cuteicus my left donut is missing, as is my right so hunt anything that moves. Sit as close as possible to warm fire without sitting on cold floor. Purr for no reason scratch at door to be let outside, get let out then scratch at door immmediately after to be let back in get my claw stuck in the dog's ear so damn that dog love blinks and purr purr purr purr yawn and sleep over your phone and make cute snoring noises walk on a keyboard. Bite plants pretend not to be evil or get video posted to internet for chasing red dot so why use post when this sofa is here for the cat was chasing the mouse hopped up on catnip. Why dog in house?
